---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import PhilosophySection from '../components/PhilosophySection.astro';
import LevelsSection from '../components/LevelsSection.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <Hero
      heading="You're not stuck. You're repeating. And that can change."
      subtext="You’re not broken. You’re repeating something you haven’t seen yet."
      ctaText="Book Your Session"
      ctaLink="/work-with-me"
    />
    <PhilosophySection
      subtitle="You’ve done the work."
      title="And yet… you keep ending in the same situations."
      paragraphs={[
        "You’ve reflected. You’ve tried to evolve. You’ve tried to “fix” things.",
        "Different job. Same tension. Different people. Same dynamics. Different effort. Same result.",
        "At some point, you start wondering: Is it me? No. It’s not just you. But it’s not random either. What you’re experiencing is not bad luck.",
        "And it’s not a lack of effort. You’re not stuck because you’re weak. You’re not stuck because you’re lazy. You’re not stuck because you “haven’t done enough work”.",
        "You’re stuck because you’re caught in patterns that didn’t start with you… But you’re the one repeating them.",
        "Until you see them clearly, you’ll keep living them. <strong class=\"font-medium text-tw-black\">Because what you don’t see, runs the show.</strong>",
      ]}
      image="/images/blur-stuck.jpg"
      imageAlt="Break the pattern"
      linkText="Understand the work"
      linkHref="/work-with-me"
    />
    <section class="py-32 bg-tw-white relative">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start">
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-tw-green"></span>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-tw-green">What this work is</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-highlight text-[18px] md:text-[24px] lg:text-[30px] tracking-tight font-medium text-tw-black leading-[1.15]">
            I don’t help you “feel better”.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-tw-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
          <p>I help you see what’s actually running your life.</p>
          <p>I help you understand the cycles that keep on repeating and interrupt them at the root.</p>
          <p>Because the problem is not just what you do or don’t do.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <LevelsSection
      title="It’s the systems in which you operate"
      subtitle="You don’t need more coping strategies. You need to see and understand the systems you’re part of."
      levels={[
        {
          title: 'Your Body',
          subtitle: 'where tension, stress, and imbalance accumulate.',
          image: '/images/xyz-shoot-axT4KncRaGc-unsplash.jpg',
          tag: 'Body',
          link: '/work-with-me',
        },
        {
          title: 'Your Family',
          subtitle: 'where patterns start, and sometimes long before you.',
          image: '/images/ty-downs-P4InE2tswBs-unsplash.jpg',
          tag: 'Family',
          link: '/work-with-me',
        },
        {
          title: 'Your Work Environment',
          subtitle: 'where these patterns play out again and again.',
          image: '/images/phil-desforges-werrs0UfZvU-unsplash.jpg',
          tag: 'Work',
          link: '/work-with-me',
        },
      ]}
    />
    <section class="py-32 bg-tw-white relative">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start">
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/me-fuck-the-pattern-home.jpg" alt="Fuck the pattern" class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover rounded-3xl" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-8 text-lg text-tw-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-tw-green"></span>
            <span class="text-[18px] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-tw-green">After this work, you don’t become “perfect”.</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-highlight text-[18px] md:text-[24px] lg:text-[30px] tracking-tight font-medium text-tw-black leading-[1.15]">
            You don’t need to become a “better version of yourself”
          </h2>
          <p>You become aware enough to stop repeating.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-tw-black font-medium">
            <li>You recognize patterns before they trap you.</li>
            <li>You stop over-adapting to situations that drain you.</li>
            <li>You make decisions that actually align with you.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Not because you forced yourself.</p>
          <p>Because the invisible chains that kept you trapped in your patterns have been brought to light and broken.</p>
          <p>And for the first time:</p>
          <p class="font-highlight text-3xl md:text-4xl text-tw-green leading-tight">Your life really stops repeating itself.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-32 bg-tw-gray-100 relative" id="contact">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-tw-green"></span>
            <span class="text-[20px] font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-tw-green">Beware</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-highlight text-[24px] md:text-[36px] tracking-tight font-medium text-tw-black leading-[1.1]">
            This is not for everyone
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
          <div class="bg-tw-gray-100 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl tracking-tight font-medium text-tw-black mb-6">This is not for you if:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-tw-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
              <li>you want quick fixes</li>
              <li>you prefer staying comfortable in what you already know</li>
              <li>you’re not ready to question your own patterns</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-tw-black text-white rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl tracking-tight font-medium mb-6">This is for you if:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-white/75 font-light leading-relaxed">
              <li>you’re tired of repeating the same story</li>
              <li>you’re ready to see what’s actually there, even if you don’t like it</li>
              <li>you want real change, not just insight</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/work-with-me" class="inline-flex bg-tw-yellow text-tw-black px-10 py-5 rounded-full items-center gap-3 text-lg hover:bg-tw-yellow/80 transition-colors group font-medium">
          <span class="text-base tracking-wide uppercase">Book your session</span>
          <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-5 h-5 stroke-[1.5] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
